values.comment:
Encode a YAML record.

   toString 0 (record [ ( "name", string "Sally" )
                      , ( "height", int 187)
                      ]
              )
   --> "{name: Sally,height: 187}"

   toString 2 (record [ ( "foo", int 42 )
                      , ( "bar", float 3.14 )
                      ]
              )
   --> "foo: 42\nbar: 3.14"
